title: Orbital - Satan THREE - UK exclusive
description:
Satan (Industry Standard Edit)
Chime (Recorded Live At The V96 Festival, Chelmsford)
Impact (Recorded Live At The V96 Festival, Chelmsford) 


Recorded with crowd noise.


All tracks written, produced and performed by P&P Hartnoll.
Cut by Geoff Pesche.
Live Crew: Micky Mann, Luke Losey, Giles Thacker, Alisdair "Rock" Young, Jackie Bracey, Lee Walker, Ivan Kushlik, Jonny Gaskil, Andy James, Scott "Stodge" Stoddard, Ian Whirrel, Pete Skan, Gragham Skan, Jamie Skan, Chris Skan, Kenny Ken Kirklaldy and Harpo.



Note the 666 on the edge of the cd case.
